item.title: Introduction
item.description: I listen to music now and then and then some more. Now and then I get stuck into a vicious listening cycle, where I listen to same songs over and over again. In an attempt to increase and diversify my music tastes, I have been listening to a new album every week and Iâ€™ll try to jot down my feelings here. Pop and rock have always been my go-to genres, mostly leaning towards rock.
